Other third-party components
================================================================================

Workprint vendors a reviewed copy of the `unslop-text` scanner from the
`vibecoded-design-tells` project (MIT License, copyright JCarterJohnson).
See third_party/vibecoded-design-tells/NOTICE.md and
third_party/vibecoded-design-tells/LICENSE for full attribution and license
terms.

Workprint's optional `claude-desktop-chat` extra depends on
`ccl_chromium_reader` (cclgroupltd/ccl_chromium_reader), installed directly
from its own repository at a pinned commit rather than vendored into this
repository. See that project's own repository for its license terms.
